# Example O3 Linux package signature evidence

Copy to `../linux-sig.txt` only after a real detached signature on the freeze artifact.
This example file is **not** gather PASS evidence.

```
artifact: dist/1.0.0/linux-x64/trareon-lab-linux-x64.tar.gz
sha256: REPLACE
signature: dist/1.0.0/linux-x64/trareon-lab-linux-x64.tar.gz.asc
gpg_verify: PASS
pubkey_fingerprint: REPLACE (must match ../linux-signing-pubkey.asc)
signed_utc: REPLACE
operator: REPLACE
```

Also place the **public** key only at `../linux-signing-pubkey.asc` per `docs/LINUX-PACKAGE-SIGNING-KEY-PLAN.md`.
